            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3ELeviticus%2015%3A1-16%3A28%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_15_1%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3ELeviticus%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EBodily%20Discharges%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Moses%20and%20Aaron%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_15_2%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGive%20the%20following%20instructions%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BAny%20man%20who%20has%20a%20bodily%20discharge%20is%20ceremonially%20unclean.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_15_3%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20defilement%20is%20caused%20by%20his%20discharge%2C%20whether%20the%20discharge%20continues%20or%20stops.%20In%20either%20case%20the%20man%20is%20unclean.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_15_4%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EAny%20bed%20on%20which%20the%20man%20with%20the%20discharge%20lies%20and%20anything%20on%20which%20he%20sits%20will%20be%20ceremonially%20unclean.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22levi_15_5%22%20bk%3D%22levi%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20if%20you%20touch%20the%20man%26%23x2019%3Bs%20bed%2C%20you%20must%20wash%20your%20clothes%20and%20bathe%20yourself%20in%20water%2C%20and%20you%20will%20remain%20unclean%20un